reviews.review_text: Fun This is a very energetic show, featuring an excellent first set that never seems to slow down or grow lethargic.  The second set isn't bad, but also isn't really anything special, and Jerry's singing starts taking a turn for the worse when Comes a Time rolls around.  Overall, though, this is a fun, energetic show – one to remember.
